		<content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:list {"ordered":true} -->
<ol id="sensei-quiz-list" class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Why is it advised to set up 301 redirects when migrating a website?<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>To optimize media content</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>To improve website security</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>To maintain search engine rankings, traffic, and conversions</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>To migrate to a new host and domain, begin by setting up a new site and installing a migration plugin on both your old and new websites. Additionally, ensure to back up your site on a device before proceeding with the migration.<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>True</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>False</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>What are some reasons why someone might want to migrate their website? Select all that apply.<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Moving to a new host</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Having versions of the same site</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Moving from HTTP to HTTPS</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Changing your domain name</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>What is the purpose of using a migration plugin?<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list"><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>To create a backup of the website</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>To transfer the website to a new host and domain</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item -->

<!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>To improve website performance</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<!-- /wp:list --></li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ol>
<!-- /wp:list -->]]></content:encoded>
